description:
Another day, another pointless announcement from Disney Lucasfilm, for a Star Wars project that will probably never happen. In this case, a whole new trilogy of movies overseen by Simon Kinberg. What are the chances this will ever actually happen?

Get your Drinker plushes here: https://www.makeship.com/shop/creator/the-critical-drinker
title: ENOUGH With The Star Wars Announcements!
